    "created_at": "2015-11-09T14:04:33Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-11-09T14:04:33Z",
    "body": "Until this is fixed it's possible to tweak the menu label text for _Edit_ and _View_ so that no unwanted additional entries are made. In my case I just added '\\u200C' to the view menu label text. This is the zero width non-joiner character which is invisible, so the menu item will look the same as without the character. This worked for me on OS X El Capitan.\n"
